de language“smartness”features like code completion, find references, etc. for clients such as C/C++ Editors."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"简单来说，clangd 是 Clang 对语言服务器协定（Language Server Protocol）的实现，提供了一些智能的特性，例如全项目索引、代码跳转、变量重命名、更快的代码补全、提示信息、格式化代码等，并且能利用 LSP 与 Vim、Emacs、VSCode 等编辑器协作。虽然官方给出的定义是 LSP 的实现，但 clangd 的功能更接近语言服务器（Language Server）而不仅仅只是协议本身。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"VS Code 的 C/C++ 插件也有自动补全等功能，但在提示信息的易读程度的准确度等方面与 clangd 相比稍逊一筹，所以我们有时会使用 clangd 代替 C/C++ 插件来实现代码自动补全等功能。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"安装"},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"className":["anchor"],"id":"安装"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85","ariaLabel":"安装 permalink","className":["anchorLink","after"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Linux 用户可以直接用内置的包管理器安装 clangd，各个发行版的操作大同小异。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"有的发行版只需要安装 clang。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n\n"},{"type":"eleme